Hello team,

We need to implement the FR VAT for the following locations:

Rhenus Forest Logistics GmbH & Co. KG 4200040000
Rhenus Forest Logistics GmbH & Co. KG 4200050000
Rhenus Forest Logistics GmbH & Co. KG 4200060000

The following VAT needs to be implemented:
 * Regular (tax key: LJ)
 * Reduced (tax key: LK)
 * reduced_2 (tax key: L5)
